: off São Paulo and Santa Catarina states, 
<quantity id="4CC79B34FFD7FFF5F9E625D1FB89F953" box="[926,1059,1754,1780]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.205" metricValueMax="1.4" metricValueMin="1.01" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" unit="m" value="120.5" valueMax="140.0" valueMin="101.0">101–140 m</quantity>
(present study).
